---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
---

<div class="flex flex-col space-y-2 pt-4 pb-8 text-lg text-gray-600">
  <div class="flex space-x-2 items-end">
    <span>
      <Icon name="pencil" class="w-16 text-orange-500" />
    </span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl text-gray-500 font-medium">Welcome to write-tight!</h1>
  </div>
  <p>
    The goal of write-tight is to improve your writing so you can say exactly
    what you want with precision and power. Write-tight analyzes writing
    patterns which are based on books and courses on professional writing. These
    rules are expressed with spaCy rule-based matching.
  </p>
  <p>
    To deepen the understanding of your writing patterns the Part of Speech
    (POS) tags are also shown and explained (<a
      class="text-blue-500 underline px-1"
      href="https://universaldependencies.org/u/pos/"
      target="_blank"
      tabindex="-1">source</a
    >).
  </p>
</div>
